{"title":"父子篇","authors":["黄树则"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":12,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"父子篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄树则"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在童年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就懂得了祖国的苦难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在解救祖国的斗争中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲洒尽了自己的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲走在霜重的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在残月的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着西风正烈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他到国外读书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归来时已经是英俊青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能说一口流利的俄语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在延安和父亲相见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你去学种地！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲说，“和农民做了知心朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过惯了农民生活，再来看我。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是他换上草鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背起被包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻山越岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进农民的家庭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国解放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲没有让他想到安乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是让他跟随志愿军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到朝鲜战场去经受烽火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他英勇地战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到付出他年轻的生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临终的一刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他的心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮现着父亲的高大身影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他至死牢记父亲的话语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人民交给你一副扁担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你担起往前走吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路程还会很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且不会平坦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必我再三叮嘱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要做一个合格的共产党员！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他叫毛岸英，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东是他的父亲。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}